label: timestamp
comment: Last reported time of observation from the vehicle. SameAs: 'timestamp' field from GTFS Realtime message-Vehicleposition (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-vehicleposition)

label: current_status
comment: Vehicle status Indiaction to denote if the bus is InTransit(Running), haulted at a stop or idle at a depot.SameAs: 'current_status' field from GTFS Realtime message-Vehicleposition (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-vehicleposition)

label: trip_id
comment: Trip ID/Trip name alloted to the bus corresponding to this observation, in consideration to the time of the day and the direction of the trip on the given routeId. SameAs: 'trip_id' field from GTFS Realtime message-TripDescriptor (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-tripdescriptor)

label: stop_id
comment: Stop ID/Stop name of the bus stops corresponding to the bus in this observation. SameAs: 'stop_id' field from GTFS Realtime message-Vehicleposition (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-vehicleposition)

label: route_id
comment: Route ID assigned to the route on which the bus/vehicle corresponding to the bus in this observation is currently plying on. SameAs: 'route_id' field from GTFS Realtime message-TripDescriptor (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-tripdescriptor)

label: stop_name
comment: Describes the name of the Bus Stop. SameAs: 'stop_name' field from GTFS Static Field definitions-stops.txt (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs/reference#stopstxt)

label: current_stop_sequence
comment: Sequence ID/sequence number for the current stop along the designated route. SameAs: 'current_stop_sequence' field from GTFS Realtime message-Vehicleposition (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-vehicleposition)

label: route_short_name
comment: Short name of a route. This will often be the transit vehicle's board name like "402D",  or "Green" that riders use to identify a route. SameAs: 'route_short_name' field from GTFS Static Field definitions-routes.txt (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs/reference#routestxt)

label: route_long_name
comment: Full name of a route. This name is more descriptive than the routeShortName and often includes the route's destination or stop. This mostly includes the to and from destination names of the route. SameAs: 'route_long_name' field from GTFS Static Field definitions-routes.txt (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs/reference#routestxt)

label: route_desc
comment: Description of the route. This can include the entire route details including to and from destination and timing information in a text description form. SameAs: 'route_desc' field from GTFS Static Field definitions-routes.txt (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs/reference#routestxt)

label: route_type
comment:
Number indicating the type of transport-
1 - Subway, Metro. Any underground rail system within a metropolitan area.
2 - Rail. Used for intercity or long-distance travel.
3 - Bus. Used for short- and long-distance bus routes. 
SameAs: 'route_type' field from GTFS Static Field definitions-routes.txt (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs/reference#routestxt)

label: vehicle_id
comment: Name of the bus/vehicle corresponding to this observation. SameAs: 'id' field from GTFS Realtime message-VehicleDescriptor (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-vehicledescriptor)

label: license_plate
comment: Gives the License Plate number of the vehice. SameAs: 'license_plate' field from GTFS Realtime message-VehicleDescriptor (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-vehicledescriptor)

label: schedule_relationship
comment: Describes if the Route/Trip has been scheduled. SameAs: 'schedule_relationship' field from enumScheduleRelationship (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#enum-schedulerelationship-2)

label: position
comment: Gives the current position of the vehicle. SameAs:'Position' from GTFS- Realtime message-Position  (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-position)

label: latitude
comment: Current latitude position obtained from the bus/vehicle corresponding to this observation. SameAs 'latitude' from GTFS- Realtime message-Position  (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-position)

label: longitude
comment: Current longitude position obtained from the bus/vehicle corresponding to this observation. SameAs 'longitude' from GTFS- Realtime message-Position  (https://developers.google.com/transit/gtfs-realtime/reference#message-position)
